# CHANGE

## 1.0.0 - 2026-05-07

- Initial public release of Music2DBridge.
- Added realtime microphone audio analysis pipeline (pitch, energy, note class, chord, key).
- Added VTube Studio WebSocket integration with authentication token caching.
- Added automatic custom-parameter creation in VTube Studio for bridge parameters.
- Added dual note output modes:
  - `class`: single parameter `ParamInstNoteClass` with values `0..11`.
  - `per-note`: per-note parameters `ParamInstNoteC` ... `ParamInstNoteB` with values `0..1`.
- Added fixed-key filter support via CLI/env (`--fixed-key`, `M2D_FIXED_KEY`).
- Added cross-platform Avalonia desktop UI with Start/Stop controls and runtime log.
- Added UI note-mode selector (`class` / `per-note`).
- Added UI input-device selector with `System Default` fallback to OS default capture device.
- Added CLI mode support from the same executable via `--cli`.
- Added input-device selection via CLI/env (`--input-device`, `M2D_INPUT_DEVICE`).
- Added Windows WASAPI shared-mode capture backend for multi-app input sharing.
- Improved compatibility with guitar workflows using ASIO host/routing alongside Music2DBridge.
- Added plugin icon support for VTube Studio auth prompt (128x128 PNG Base64).
- Added app icon configuration for normal build/publish outputs.
- Added GitHub Actions release workflow on tag push, publishing Windows/Linux/macOS artifacts.
